Package: ldapr
Type: Package
Title: An R implementation of LDAP
Version: 0.0.2
Date: 2022-09-24
Authors@R: person("Liam", "Gilbey", email = "liam.gilbey@gmail.com",
  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An implementation of LDAP in R. This allows authentication against a valid LDAP server, which is mostly useful inside a 
  shiny application that requires use authentication.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Imports: Rcpp (>= 1.0.1),
  R6
LinkingTo: Rcpp
RoxygenNote: 7.2.1
SystemRequirements: libldap-2.4-2 (deb)
